schemeContent.detailedDescription_md:
The scheme &amp;quot;Credit Linked Subsidy Scheme for Middle Income Group (CLSS for MIG)&amp;quot; by the Ministry of Housing and Urban Affairs, Government of India aims to provide interest subsidy on housing loans to Middle Income Group families. CLSS for MIG will be implemented initially in 2017 for a period of one-year w.e.f. 01 January 2017. This will also be implemented as a Central Sector Scheme. Under the Scheme, beneficiaries of the Middle-Income Group (MIG) can seek housing loans from Banks, Housing Finance Companies, and other such institutions for the acquisition/ construction of houses (including re-purchase).
